(63,9,'_content_backup_fontsize','<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#2d1b00\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"100%\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background-color:#2d1b00;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\">\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"5rem\",\"bottom\":\"4rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"gradient\":\"linear-gradient(135deg,#556B2F 0%,#2d1b00 50%,#4B0082 100%)\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"800px\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#556B2F 0%,#2d1b00 50%,#4B0082 100%);padding-top:5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:4rem;padding-left:2rem\">\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"3.2rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"}}} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-size:3.2rem;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">La Science Quantique</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffdbb5\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.2rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffdbb5;font-size:1.2rem;line-height:1.8\">Des decennies de recherche en physique vibratoire appliquee a l\'hygiene domestique.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"4rem\",\"bottom\":\"4rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#3d2b1f\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"800px\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background-color:#3d2b1f;padding-top:4rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:4rem;padding-left:2rem\">\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.8rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:1.8rem;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">Le Principe de Superposition Poussiereuse</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#d4b896\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#d4b896;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.8\">Selon le principe de Heisenberg, on ne peut pas connaitre simultanement la position et la salete d\'une particule de poussiere. Nos aspirateurs exploitent cette incertitude : en observant la poussiere avec un capteur quantique brevete, ils la forcent a choisir entre etre sale ou etre quelque part. Elle choisit invariablement de ne plus etre sale.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#C9A84C\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#C9A84C;color:#C9A84C\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.8rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:1.8rem;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">L\'Intrication Domestique</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#d4b896\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#d4b896;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.8\">Lorsque deux grains de poussiere ont cohabite sous votre canape, ils deviennent quantiquement intriques. Purifier l\'un purifie instantanement l\'autre, ou qu\'il se trouve dans l\'univers. C\'est pourquoi nos clients rapportent souvent que la maison de leur belle-mere devient mysterieusement plus propre apres l\'achat d\'un de nos aspirateurs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#C9A84C\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#C9A84C;color:#C9A84C\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.8rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:1.8rem;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">Le Filtre de Schrödinger</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#d4b896\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#d4b896;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.8\">Notre filtre HEPA-Q (Haute Efficacite Paranormale et Astrale - Quantique) place chaque particule dans un etat de superposition entre \"propre\" et \"sale\". Tant que vous n\'ouvrez pas le sac, la poussiere est simultanement purifiee et non purifiee. Nous vous recommandons donc de ne jamais ouvrir le sac. Jamais.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#C9A84C\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#C9A84C;color:#C9A84C\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.8rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:1.8rem;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">La Formule Fondamentale</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#BA55D3\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.4rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"lineHeight\":\"2.2\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#BA55D3;font-size:1.4rem;font-style:italic;line-height:2.2\">P(proprete) = h x f(karma) / m(poussiere) x c(conscience)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#C9A84C\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"0.85rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.6\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#C9A84C;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.6\">ou h = constante de Harmony, f = frequence karmique, m = masse poussiereuse, c = coefficient de conscience. Publication en attente dans la revue \"Nature Astrale\" depuis 1974.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->'),
