(38,0,'2026-02-21 01:23:23','2026-02-21 00:23:23','<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#2d1b00\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"100%\"}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background-color:#2d1b00;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\">nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"5rem\",\"bottom\":\"4rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"gradient\":\"linear-gradient(135deg,#556B2F 0%,#2d1b00 50%,#4B0082 100%)\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"800px\"}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#556B2F 0%,#2d1b00 50%,#4B0082 100%);padding-top:5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:4rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"}}} -->n<h1 class=\"fs-320 wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">La Science Quantique</h1>n<!-- /wp:heading -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffdbb5\"},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-120 has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffdbb5;line-height:1.8\">Des decennies de recherche en physique vibratoire appliquee a l\'hygiene domestique.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"4rem\",\"bottom\":\"4rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#3d2b1f\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"800px\"}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background-color:#3d2b1f;padding-top:5rem;padding-right:3rem;padding-bottom:5rem;padding-left:3rem\">nn<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->n<h2 class=\"fs-180 wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">Le Principe de Superposition Poussiereuse</h2>n<!-- /wp:heading -->nn<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-100 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;line-height:1.8\">Selon le principe de Heisenberg, on ne peut pas connaitre simultanement la position et la salete d\'une particule de poussiere. Nos aspirateurs exploitent cette incertitude : en observant la poussiere avec un capteur quantique brevete, ils la forcent a choisir entre etre sale ou etre quelque part. Elle choisit invariablement de ne plus etre sale.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->nn<!-- wp:separator {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#C9A84C\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#C9A84C;color:#C9A84C\"/>n<!-- /wp:separator -->nn<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->n<h2 class=\"fs-180 wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">L\'Intrication Domestique</h2>n<!-- /wp:heading -->nn<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-100 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;line-height:1.8\">Lorsque deux grains de poussiere ont cohabite sous votre canape, ils deviennent quantiquement intriques. Purifier l\'un purifie instantanement l\'autre, ou qu\'il se trouve dans l\'univers. C\'est pourquoi nos clients rapportent souvent que la maison de leur belle-mere devient mysterieusement plus propre apres l\'achat d\'un de nos aspirateurs.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->nn<!-- wp:separator {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#C9A84C\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#C9A84C;color:#C9A84C\"/>n<!-- /wp:separator -->nn<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->n<h2 class=\"fs-180 wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">Le Filtre de Schrödinger</h2>n<!-- /wp:heading -->nn<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-100 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;line-height:1.8\">Notre filtre HEPA-Q (Haute Efficacite Paranormale et Astrale - Quantique) place chaque particule dans un etat de superposition entre \"propre\" et \"sale\". Tant que vous n\'ouvrez pas le sac, la poussiere est simultanement purifiee et non purifiee. Nous vous recommandons donc de ne jamais ouvrir le sac. Jamais.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->nn<!-- wp:separator {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#C9A84C\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#C9A84C;color:#C9A84C\"/>n<!-- /wp:separator -->nn<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->n<h2 class=\"fs-180 wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">La Formule Fondamentale</h2>n<!-- /wp:heading -->nn<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#BA55D3\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"lineHeight\":\"2.2\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-140 has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#BA55D3;font-style:italic;line-height:2.2\">P(proprete) = h x f(karma) / m(poussiere) x c(conscience)</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->nn<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#C9A84C\"},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.6\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-085 has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#C9A84C;line-height:1.6\">ou h = constante de Harmony, f = frequence karmique, m = masse poussiereuse, c = coefficient de conscience. Publication en attente dans la revue \"Nature Astrale\" depuis 1974.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->nn</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->','La Science Quantique','','inherit','closed','closed','','9-revision-v1','','','2026-02-21 01:23:23','2026-02-21 00:23:23','',9,'http://192.168.1.17/wptest/?p=38',0,'revision','',0),
