ft:3rem\">nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2rem\",\"bottom\":\"2rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"border\":{\"left\":{\"color\":\"#DAA520\",\"width\":\"3px\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"}}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-left-color:#DAA520;border-left-width:3px;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:2rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:2rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-105 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-style:italic;line-height:1.8\">\"Depuis que j\'aspire quantiquement, mes plantes me parlent. Le ficus m\'a remercie mardi. Le cactus reste silencieux mais je sens qu\'il pense fort.\"</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"1rem\"}}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-090 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-top:1rem;\">-- Gisele, 67 ans, Carpentras, proprietaire du Quantum 3000</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2rem\",\"bottom\":\"2rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"border\":{\"left\":{\"color\":\"#7CFC00\",\"width\":\"3px\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"}}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-left-color:#7CFC00;border-left-width:3px;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:2rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:2rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-105 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-style:italic;line-height:1.8\">\"La poussiere redeposee est tellement plus zen. Avant, elle s\'accumulait n\'importe comment, sans conscience. Maintenant elle se place en formation mandala sous le lit. C\'est bouleversant.\"</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#7CFC00\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"1rem\"}}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-090 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#7CFC00;margin-top:1rem;\">-- Jean-Pierre, 54 ans, plateau du Larzac, Chakra Clean 5000</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2rem\",\"bottom\":\"2rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"border\":{\"left\":{\"color\":\"#D084E8\",\"width\":\"3px\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"}}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-left-color:#D084E8;border-left-width:3px;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:2rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:2rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-105 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-style:italic;line-height:1.8\">\"Mon aura n\'a jamais ete aussi propre. Mon therapeute dit que mes frequences vibratoires ont augmente de 47%. Mon ex-femme dit que je suis toujours aussi penible, mais quantiquement, je sais que j\'ai evolue.\"</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#D084E8\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"1rem\"}}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-090 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#D084E8;margin-top:1rem;\">-- Moonbeam (anciennement Patrick), 42 ans, Ibiza, Nirvana Dust 7000</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2rem\",\"bottom\":\"2rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"border\":{\"left\":{\"color\":\"#FFD700\",\"width\":\"3px\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"}}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-left-color:#FFD700;border-left-width:3px;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:2rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:2rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-105 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-style:italic;line-height:1.8\">\"J\'ai achete le Cosmic Vortex 9000 Pro. Quand je l\'ai allume, mon chat a levite pendant 3 secondes. Je ne suis pas sure que ce soit une fonctionnalite prevue mais il a l\'air d\'avoir apprecie. Il ronronne maintenant en La bemol, la frequence de la guerison universelle.\"</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#FFD700\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"1rem\"}}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-090 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#FFD700;margin-top:1rem;\">-- Sylviane, 59 ans, Aix-en-Provence, Cosmic Vortex 9000 Pro</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2rem\",\"bottom\":\"2rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"border\":{\"left\":{\"color\":\"#E8935A\",\"width\":\"3px\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"}}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-left-color:#D2691E;border-left-width:3px;background-color:#4a3728;padding-top:2rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:2rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-105 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-style:italic;line-height:1.8\">\"J\'etais sceptique. Physicien au CNRS, je pensais que c\'etait n\'importe quoi. Puis j\'ai essaye. Je ne comprends toujours pas comment ca marche, mais ma femme dit que la maison n\'a jamais ete aussi propre. J\'ai demissionne. Je vends des cristaux maintenant.\"</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#E8935A\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"1rem\"}}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-090 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#E8935A;margin-top:1rem;\">-- Dr. Bernard Mouton, ancien chercheur au CNRS, desormais Chaman-Aspirologue</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->','Temoignages Cosmiques','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-revision-v1','','','2026-02-21 01:23:25','2026-02-21 00:23:25','',10,'http://192.168.1.17/wptest/?p=40',0,'revision','',0),
