(42,0,'2026-02-21 01:23:27','2026-02-21 00:23:27','<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#2d1b00\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"100%\"}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background-color:#2d1b00;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\">nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"5rem\",\"bottom\":\"4rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"gradient\":\"linear-gradient(135deg,#8B4513 0%,#4B0082 50%,#556B2F 100%)\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"800px\"}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8B4513 0%,#4B0082 50%,#556B2F 100%);padding-top:5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:4rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"}}} -->n<h1 class=\"fs-320 wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">Le Rituel d\'Aspiration</h1>n<!-- /wp:heading -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffdbb5\"},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-120 has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffdbb5;line-height:1.8\">Aspirer n\'est pas nettoyer. C\'est un acte sacre de communion avec la matiere.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"4rem\",\"bottom\":\"4rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#3d2b1f\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"800px\"}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background-color:#3d2b1f;padding-top:5rem;padding-right:3rem;padding-bottom:5rem;padding-left:3rem\">nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"1.5rem\",\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"1rem\"}}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-radius:1rem;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->n<h2 class=\"fs-150 wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">Etape 1 -- La Preparation Astrale</h2>n<!-- /wp:heading -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-100 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;line-height:1.8\">Allumez trois bougies en cire d\'abeille bio. Disposez-les en triangle equilateral autour de l\'aspirateur. Faites bruler de la sauge blanche. Si le detecteur de fumee se declenche, c\'est que votre maison expulse ses energies negatives. Bon signe.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"1.5rem\",\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"1rem\"}}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-radius:1rem;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#7CFC00\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->n<h2 class=\"fs-150 wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#7CFC00;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">Etape 2 -- L\'Invocation du Vide</h2>n<!-- /wp:heading -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-100 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;line-height:1.8\">Avant de brancher l\'appareil, posez vos deux mains sur le capot et recitez le mantra d\'activation : \"Om Vacuum Padme Hum\". Repetez trois fois. Vous devriez sentir une legere vibration. Si vous ne sentez rien, verifiez que l\'appareil est bien branche.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"1.5rem\",\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"1rem\"}}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-radius:1rem;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#D084E8\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->n<h2 class=\"fs-150 wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#D084E8;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">Etape 3 -- La Danse Aspiratoire</h2>n<!-- /wp:heading -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-100 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;line-height:1.8\">Ne passez jamais l\'aspirateur en ligne droite. Le mouvement doit dessiner des spirales, dans le sens inverse des aiguilles d\'une montre dans l\'hemisphere nord (sens horaire en Australie). La spirale est la forme sacree de l\'univers. Votre sol le sait. Respectez-le.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"1.5rem\",\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"1rem\"}}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-radius:1rem;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#E8935A\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->n<h2 class=\"fs-150 wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#E8935A;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">Etape 4 -- La Redeposition Consciente</h2>n<!-- /wp:heading -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-100 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;line-height:1.8\">Appuyez sur le bouton \"Redepose Karmique\" (le doré). L\'aspirateur va redistribuer la poussiere purifiee dans votre interieur. Ne vous inquietez pas si ca ressemble exactement a de la poussiere normale. La transformation est au niveau sub-atomique. Faites confiance au processus.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"1.5rem\",\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"1rem\"}}} -->n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-radius:1rem;background-color:#4a3728;padding-top:1.5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;padding-left:2rem\">n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#FFD700\"},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->n<h2 class=\"fs-150 wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#FFD700;font-style:italic;font-weight:300\">Etape 5 -- La Gratitude Post-Aspiratoire</h2>n<!-- /wp:heading -->n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->n<p class=\"fs-100 has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;line-height:1.8\">Eteignez l\'aspirateur. Remerciez-le a voix haute. Remerciez la poussiere pour son voyage transformationnel. Remerciez votre sol. Remerciez-vous. Buvez une tisane de camomille quantique (vendue separement, 27 euros les 30g). Namaste.</p>n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->n</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->nn</div>n<!-- /wp:group -->','Le Rituel','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2026-02-21 01:23:27','2026-02-21 00:23:27','',11,'http://192.168.1.17/wptest/?p=42',0,'revision','',0),
