f;padding-top:5rem;padding-right:3rem;padding-bottom:5rem;padding-left:3rem\">\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"1.5rem\",\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"1rem\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-radius:1rem;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;padding-left:2rem\">\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.5rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;font-size:1.5rem;font-style:italic\">Etape 1 -- La Preparation Astrale</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.8\">Allumez trois bougies en cire d\'abeille bio. Disposez-les en triangle equilateral autour de l\'aspirateur. Faites bruler de la sauge blanche. Si le detecteur de fumee se declenche, c\'est que votre maison expulse ses energies negatives. Bon signe.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"1.5rem\",\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"1rem\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-radius:1rem;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;padding-left:2rem\">\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#7CFC00\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.5rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#7CFC00;font-size:1.5rem;font-style:italic\">Etape 2 -- L\'Invocation du Vide</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.8\">Avant de brancher l\'appareil, posez vos deux mains sur le capot et recitez le mantra d\'activation : \"Om Vacuum Padme Hum\". Repetez trois fois. Vous devriez sentir une legere vibration. Si vous ne sentez rien, verifiez que l\'appareil est bien branche.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"1.5rem\",\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"1rem\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-radius:1rem;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;padding-left:2rem\">\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#D084E8\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.5rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#D084E8;font-size:1.5rem;font-style:italic\">Etape 3 -- La Danse Aspiratoire</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.8\">Ne passez jamais l\'aspirateur en ligne droite. Le mouvement doit dessiner des spirales, dans le sens inverse des aiguilles d\'une montre dans l\'hemisphere nord (sens horaire en Australie). La spirale est la forme sacree de l\'univers. Votre sol le sait. Respectez-le.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"1.5rem\",\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"1rem\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-radius:1rem;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;padding-left:2rem\">\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#E8935A\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.5rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#E8935A;font-size:1.5rem;font-style:italic\">Etape 4 -- La Redeposition Consciente</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.8\">Appuyez sur le bouton \"Redepose Karmique\" (le doré). L\'aspirateur va redistribuer la poussiere purifiee dans votre interieur. Ne vous inquietez pas si ca ressemble exactement a de la poussiere normale. La transformation est au niveau sub-atomique. Faites confiance au processus.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"1.5rem\",\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"1rem\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-radius:1rem;background-color:#4a3728;padding-top:1.5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;padding-left:2rem\">\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#FFD700\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.5rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#FFD700;font-size:1.5rem;font-style:italic\">Etape 5 -- La Gratitude Post-Aspiratoire</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.8\">Eteignez l\'aspirateur. Remerciez-le a voix haute. Remerciez la poussiere pour son voyage transformationnel. Remerciez votre sol. Remerciez-vous. Buvez une tisane de camomille quantique (vendue separement, 27 euros les 30g). Namaste.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','Le Rituel','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2026-02-21 01:55:02','2026-02-21 00:55:02','',11,'http://192.168.1.17/wptest/?p=59',0,'revision','',0),
