c\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-size:1.15rem;font-style:italic;line-height:1.8\">\"La poussiere redeposee est tellement plus zen. Avant, elle s\'accumulait n\'importe comment, sans conscience. Maintenant elle se place en formation mandala sous le lit. C\'est bouleversant.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#7CFC00\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"0.9rem\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"1rem\"}}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#7CFC00;margin-top:1rem;font-size:1.15rem\">-- Jean-Pierre, 54 ans, plateau du Larzac, Chakra Clean 5000</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2rem\",\"bottom\":\"2rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"border\":{\"left\":{\"color\":\"#D084E8\",\"width\":\"3px\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-left-color:#D084E8;border-left-width:3px;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:2rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:2rem;padding-left:2rem\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.05rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-size:1.15rem;font-style:italic;line-height:1.8\">\"Mon aura n\'a jamais ete aussi propre. Mon therapeute dit que mes frequences vibratoires ont augmente de 47%. Mon ex-femme dit que je suis toujours aussi penible, mais quantiquement, je sais que j\'ai evolue.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#D084E8\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"0.9rem\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"1rem\"}}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#D084E8;margin-top:1rem;font-size:1.15rem\">-- Moonbeam (anciennement Patrick), 42 ans, Ibiza, Nirvana Dust 7000</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2rem\",\"bottom\":\"2rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"},\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}},\"border\":{\"left\":{\"color\":\"#FFD700\",\"width\":\"3px\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-left-color:#FFD700;border-left-width:3px;background-color:#4a3728;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-top:2rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:2rem;padding-left:2rem\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.05rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-size:1.15rem;font-style:italic;line-height:1.8\">\"J\'ai achete le Cosmic Vortex 9000 Pro. Quand je l\'ai allume, mon chat a levite pendant 3 secondes. Je ne suis pas sure que ce soit une fonctionnalite prevue mais il a l\'air d\'avoir apprecie. Il ronronne maintenant en La bemol, la frequence de la guerison universelle.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#FFD700\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"0.9rem\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"1rem\"}}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#FFD700;margin-top:1rem;font-size:1.15rem\">-- Sylviane, 59 ans, Aix-en-Provence, Cosmic Vortex 9000 Pro</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"2rem\",\"bottom\":\"2rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"border\":{\"left\":{\"color\":\"#E8935A\",\"width\":\"3px\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#4a3728\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"border-left-color:#D2691E;border-left-width:3px;background-color:#4a3728;padding-top:2rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:2rem;padding-left:2rem\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.05rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-size:1.15rem;font-style:italic;line-height:1.8\">\"J\'etais sceptique. Physicien au CNRS, je pensais que c\'etait n\'importe quoi. Puis j\'ai essaye. Je ne comprends toujours pas comment ca marche, mais ma femme dit que la maison n\'a jamais ete aussi propre. J\'ai demissionne. Je vends des cristaux maintenant.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#E8935A\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"0.9rem\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"1rem\"}}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#E8935A;margin-top:1rem;font-size:1.15rem\">-- Dr. Bernard Mouton, ancien chercheur au CNRS, desormais Chaman-Aspirologue</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','Temoignages Cosmiques','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-revision-v1','','','2026-02-21 01:55:02','2026-02-21 00:55:02','',10,'http://192.168.1.17/wptest/?p=60',0,'revision','',0),
(61,0,'2026-02-21 01:55:02','2026-02-21 00:55:02','<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#2d1b00\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"100%\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background-color:#2d1b00;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\">\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"5rem\",\"bottom\":\"4rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"gradient\":\"linear-gradient(135deg,#556B2F 0%,#2d1b00 50%,#4B0082 100%)\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"800px\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#556B2F 0%,#2d1b00 50%,#4B0082 100%);padding-top:5rem;padding-right:2rem;padding-bottom:4rem;padding-left:2rem\">\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"3.2rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffecd2\"}}} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffecd2;font-size:3.2rem;font-style:italic\">La Science Quantique</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#ffdbb5\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.2rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffdbb5;font-size:1.2rem;line-height:1.8\">Des decennies de recherche en physique vibratoire appliquee a l\'hygiene domestique.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"4rem\",\"bottom\":\"4rem\",\"left\":\"2rem\",\"right\":\"2rem\"}},\"color\":{\"background\":\"#3d2b1f\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"800px\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background\" style=\"background-color:#3d2b1f;padding-top:5rem;padding-right:3rem;padding-bottom:5rem;padding-left:3rem\">\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.8rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:1.8rem;font-style:italic\">Le Principe de Superposition Poussiereuse</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.8\">Selon le principe de Heisenberg, on ne peut pas connaitre simultanement la position et la salete d\'une particule de poussiere. Nos aspirateurs exploitent cette incertitude : en observant la poussiere avec un capteur quantique brevete, ils la forcent a choisir entre etre sale ou etre quelque part. Elle choisit invariablement de ne plus etre sale.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#C9A84C\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#C9A84C;color:#C9A84C\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.8rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:1.8rem;font-style:italic\">L\'Intrication Domestique</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.8\">Lorsque deux grains de poussiere ont cohabite sous votre canape, ils deviennent quantiquement intriques. Purifier l\'un purifie instantanement l\'autre, ou qu\'il se trouve dans l\'univers. C\'est pourquoi nos clients rapportent souvent que la maison de leur belle-mere devient mysterieusement plus propre apres l\'achat d\'un de nos aspirateurs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#C9A84C\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#C9A84C;color:#C9A84C\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.8rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:1.8rem;font-style:italic\">Le Filtre de Schrödinger</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#e0c9a6\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.8\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#e0c9a6;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.8\">Notre filtre HEPA-Q (Haute Efficacite Paranormale et Astrale - Quantique) place chaque particule dans un etat de superposition entre \"propre\" et \"sale\". Tant que vous n\'ouvrez pas le sac, la poussiere est simultanement purifiee et non purifiee. Nous vous recommandons donc de ne jamais ouvrir le sac. Jamais.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#C9A84C\"}},\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"background-color:#C9A84C;color:#C9A84C\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#DAA520\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.8rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"1.5rem\"}}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#DAA520;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:1.8rem;font-style:italic\">La Formule Fondamentale</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#BA55D3\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.4rem\",\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"lineHeight\":\"2.2\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#BA55D3;font-size:1.4rem;font-style:italic;line-height:2.2\">P(proprete) = h x f(karma) / m(poussiere) x c(conscience)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#C9A84C\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"0.85rem\",\"lineHeight\":\"1.6\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#C9A84C;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.6\">ou h = constante de Harmony, f = frequence karmique, m = masse poussiereuse, c = coefficient de conscience. Publication en attente dans la revue \"Nature Astrale\" depuis 1974.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','La Science Quantique','','inherit','closed','closed','','9-revision-v1','','','2026-02-21 01:55:02','2026-02-21 00:55:02','',9,'http://192.168.1.17/wptest/?p=61',0,'revision','',0),
